<section id="general-paths">
<title>Paths and Smart File Selection</title>
<informalexample>
<para>Settings => Preferences => General => Paths
</para>
</informalexample>
<para>Selecting the "Paths" Icon opens an interactive dialog in the large work area of the Prefences Dialog.  These text entry areas enable you to set the location of the directory &app; will Save and Load (Get) files from. The Browse buttons on the far right open a "File Selection" dialog that gives you a graphical interface to the selection. Otherwise simply enter the target directories into the text entry areas. Finally there is the option of disabling this Smart File Selection.
</para>
</section>

